          {
            "text": "A one-sentence affirmation for the start of a new family money story. The statement does not describe a future goal. It names what is already being built by the decisions being made now.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "New to affirmations? Read ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "how energy statements work",
